Samathy takes photos at events all over the country.
Works with (Pride Pics)[http://facebook.com/gaypridepics] during the 'Pride' season travling the country and capturing LGBT+ Prides.
She is a freelance photographer who is open to working with any and all to photograph events.
You can see several examples of her work with GPP and other clients on (her portfolio)[http://samathyb.imgur.com/ on Imgur

She also works with several other clients taking photos at different types of events.
Her previous clients include

* Official photographer for <a href="http://2017.inspirewit.com/">InspireWIT 2017 @ Uni of Nottingham </a> - <a href="http://imgur.com/a/gZLaC" >Photos from the event here</a>
* <a href="https://www.derbymuseums.org/locations/silk-mill"> The Silk Mill </a> for several events including mutiple 'Silk Mill conversations' sessions and prototyping workshops. The <a href="http://imgur.com/a/WFAzq"> Silk Mill Conversations Prototying Panel </a>
* a href="thenva.com"> The National Videogame Arcade </a> for Gamecity Festival 2016 and The Oliver Twins book launch: <a href="http://imgur.com/a/nunoL" >Gamecity 2016</a>, <a href="http://imgur.com/a/TMaDU">Oliver Twins </a>


Samathy shoots with the high end Nikon D7100 DSLR and a good compliment of lenses. she prefers her prime lenses with her favorite being the 35mm.
Her earlier work was shot on a Sony A230 DSLR.
